@toollean v0.1
@tool garmin
@desc Fetch fitness data from Garmin Connect — activities, training plans, heart rate, sleep, steps, and calendar. Use when the user asks about workouts, running stats, fitness progress, training plans, or health metrics from their Garmin watch/device.
@source /data/workspace/skills/garmin/SKILL.md
@example
  > cd /tmp && node /data/workspace/skills/garmin/scripts/garmin-api.cjs <command> [args]
@example
  > cd /tmp && node /data/workspace/skills/garmin/scripts/garmin-api.cjs \
@example
  > cd /tmp && npm install garmin-connect